	<h4 class="c-issue-toc__article-title" id="1477"><a href="/en/archive/2018/21-invisible-labor/extras-social-media-and-the-invisible-work-of-observing-the-other">Extras: Social Media and the Invisible Work of Observing the Other</a></h4>
	<h5 class="c-issue-toc__article-authors"><!--Author:--><a href="/en/bio?id=494">Krzysztof Świrek</a></h5>
	
				<a class="c-issue-toc__article-collapse-btn" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseDoi1477" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSummary1477" data-lexicon-show="show" data-lexicon-hide="hide">
